---
// Use Cases Section Component
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Who Uses YouTube Sentiment Analysis?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Discover how different professionals leverage sentiment insights</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Content Creators -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Content Creators</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Understand audience reactions to optimize future content, identify trending topics, and improve engagement strategies.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• Optimize video content based on feedback</li>
          <li>• Identify what resonates with viewers</li>
          <li>• Track audience sentiment over time</li>
          <li>• Improve thumbnail and title strategies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Marketers -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Marketing Teams</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Measure campaign effectiveness, monitor brand perception, and track competitor performance with data-driven insights.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• Measure campaign ROI and effectiveness</li>
          <li>• Monitor brand perception and reputation</li>
          <li>• Track competitor content performance</li>
          <li>• Identify market trends and opportunities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Researchers -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Researchers</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Conduct social media research, analyze public opinion trends, and gather insights for academic or market research.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• Study public opinion and trends</li>
          <li>• Analyze social media behavior</li>
          <li>• Gather data for academic research</li>
          <li>• Monitor cultural and social shifts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Business Owners -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Business Owners</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Understand customer feedback, improve products based on user sentiment, and make data-driven business decisions.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• Understand customer satisfaction</li>
          <li>• Improve products and services</li>
          <li>• Make data-driven decisions</li>
          <li>• Monitor industry trends</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Social Media Managers -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pink-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Social Media Managers</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Monitor social engagement, track sentiment around brand campaigns, and optimize content strategies across platforms.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• Track engagement and sentiment trends</li>
          <li>• Optimize social media content strategy</li>
          <li>• Monitor brand mentions and reactions</li>
          <li>• Identify viral content opportunities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- PR Professionals -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">PR Professionals</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Monitor public perception, track crisis communications, and measure the impact of PR campaigns and announcements.</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• Monitor public relations impact</li>
          <li>• Track crisis communication effectiveness</li>
          <li>• Measure announcement reception</li>
          <li>• Identify reputation management opportunities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>